OF
LYNDA MARY HERBERT
M.B.E.
1953 - 2012
DEVOTED WIFE, MOTHER, GRANDMOTHER
AND NURSE
FONDLY REMEMBERED AS ONE WHO
TRULY CARED

TREFOR JOHN HERBERT
